name: ANPreBidMobileForMoPub
summary: AppNexus PreBid Mobile For MoPub Framework
description: AppNexus PreBid Mobile For MoPub Framework runs directly on the device and allow app developers to access demand that may not be available from their mobile ad network. Compatible with MoPub SDK.
